<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,150,825]" pageId="6" pageNumber="437">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,727,753]" pageId="6" pageNumber="437">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was imported into Guangdong from 
<collectingCountry box="[870,946,727,753]" name="Brunei" pageId="6" pageNumber="437">Brunei</collectingCountry>
in 2003 as a biological control agent for the whitefly, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Gennadius" baseAuthorityYear="1889" box="[257,424,763,789]" class="Insecta" family="Aleyrodidae" genus="Bemisia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="437" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tabaci">
<emphasis box="[257,424,763,789]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="437">Bemisia tabaci</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. However, its establishment is still unknown. Further investigation is needed to determine whether it has established in Guangdong.
</paragraph>
